       10.1  CCCCoooonnnnvvvveeeennnnttttiiiioooonnnnssss

       The OSF/Motif Window Manager can be operated with either a    |
       2-button or a 3-button mouse by observing the conventions     |
       shown in Figure 10-1.  With a 2-button mouse, you can obtain  |
       a third button by pressing buttons 1 and 2 simultaneously.    |
       You can obtain five buttons from a 3-button mouse by press-   |
       ing buttons 1 and 2 for a fourth button and buttons 2         |
        and 3 for a fifth button.





